@startuml
autonumber
skinparam Style strictuml
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 10

box "使用者與 IDE 客戶端\n(User & IDE Client)" #LightBlue
actor "使用者\n(User)" as User
participant "瀏覽器 / IDE\n(Browser / IDE)" as Client
end box

box "JetBrains身份認證系統\n(Identity Provider - IdP)" #LightYellow
participant "IdP /授權" as IdP_Auth
participant "IdP /產生token" as IdP_Token
participant "IdP /JWKS" as IdP_JWKS
end box

box "JetBrains IDE Services 伺服器\n(License Vault)" #LightGreen
participant "IDE Services\n伺服器" as Server
end box

== 第一階段：取得授權碼 (Front-Channel) ==

User -> Client:  啟動登入 / 請求授權
activate Client

Client -> IdP_Auth:  重導向請求認證 (Redirect to IdP)\n包含參數:\n - response_type=code\n - client_id\n - redirect_uri\n - state=xyzSecureRandomString\n - scope=openid profile email groups
deactivate Client

User -> IdP_Auth:  使用者登入並授權\n(登入資訊由 IdP 驗證，不儲存於伺服器)

IdP_Auth --> Client:  發送授權碼 (Redirect to redirect_uri)\n包含參數:\n - code=splat-9876543210-authcode\n - state=xyzSecureRandomString
activate Client

Client -> Server:  傳送授權碼 (code) 與 state
activate Server

== 第二階段：交換 Token 並發放授權 (Back-Channel) ==

Server -> Server:  比對 state 防偽 (CSRF 防護)

Server -> IdP_Token:  交換 Token (HTTPS POST)\nPOST Body (x-www-form-urlencoded):\n - grant_type=authorization_code\n - code\n - redirect_uri\n - client_id\n - client_secret (密鑰安全地由伺服器保管)
activate IdP_Token

IdP_Token --> Server:  回傳 Token 響應 (Token Response)\nJSON 數據:\n - id_token\n - access_token\n - token_type: Bearer\n - expires_in: 3600
deactivate IdP_Token

Server -> IdP_JWKS:  請求公開金鑰驗證簽章
activate IdP_JWKS
IdP_JWKS --> Server:  回傳 JWKS (IdP 公開金鑰)
deactivate IdP_JWKS

Server -> Server:  本地解析與授權驗證\n - 驗證 ID Token (JWT) 簽章與有效期\n - 提取使用者 email / groups\n - 執行群組匹配\n   (例: RND-IntelliJ-Users -> IntelliJ Pack)

Server --> Client:  發放本地授權憑證\n(Local License Ticket)
deactivate Server

Client --> User:  啟動 IDE 成功
deactivate Client

@enduml
